{"tid":1214798,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位愛香港嘅人，你哋可唔可以試吓祈禱。","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T05:38:21.000Z","uid":243527,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"03cce2c6a0b99ab112d9fe310a894c157f06e283","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">首先搵一個安靜嘅地方<br />\n雙手合十<br />\n閉上眼睛<br />\n平靜你嘅心情<br />\n然後開始向上帝祈求</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n(Part1)<br />\n句式可以根據下述：<br />\n我們在天上的父<br />\n願人都尊祢的名為聖<br />\n願祢的國降臨<br />\n願祢的旨意行在地上<br />\n如同行在天上<br />\n我們日用的飲食<br />\n今日賜給我們<br />\n免我們的債<br />\n如同我們免了人的債<br />\n不叫我們遇見試探<br />\n救我們脫離凶惡<br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀<br />\n全是你的，直到永遠 ，阿門。</span><br />\n[size=4]<span style=\"color: pink;\">(Part 2)<br />\n我全能嘅上帝，求你保守香港，<br />\n保護所有嘅香港市民，<br />\n上街嘅市民不要讓佢哋身體受到傷害<br />\n家中嘅市民不要讓佢哋不安<br />\n亦希望你讓警察行事要有良心<br />\n不要挑起是非，騷動情緒，<br />\n再者，希望你差派聖靈告知特首<br />\n要以市民為本，要以公義行事，<br />\n不作不彰顯你國度嘅事情，可以撤回惡法。<br />\n物資方面，求你給予我地充足嘅物資<br />\n能夠應付基本所需。<br />\n體能方面，希望你賜我哋有足夠嘅體力，<br />\n堅守到底，奉主耶穌基督得勝名字祈求，阿門<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">希望你哋利用以上嘅禱告可以為香港祝福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">服用須知:</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n  <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n  每日祈禱兩次<br />\n  早晚各一次<br />\n  可以因應訴求自行改變服用次數，內容<br />\n（但part 1必須存在，part 2可自行修改訴求）<br />\n不可少於一次</span></span>"},{"pid":"069b410c572c566af5cd87566a99a8c8aee687d5","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d56751493809123d21bd9541ea2e2a016507c35","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"希望你哋真係可以嘗試吓"},{"pid":"51d6ed9a622d0409b6734e68986330efc8a9c0d0","tid":1214798,"uid":204401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:21:52.000Z","msg":"會試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e605a045e21a3bb6111ff84aa97d7f6945314167","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"好想香港可以快啲回復"},{"pid":"82bc47eb816c8fbfd5c1a59604d604bc4a828ca0","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"推比多啲人睇多啲人試"},{"pid":"9719e4f7fa07ed78c06d06ca3518c939e247a888","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:22:35.000Z","msg":"祈禱好需要大家團結"},{"pid":"06ecaadfd72e31ccef727480ef44190636c5536e","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:22:47.000Z","msg":"如果有家人可以捉住佢哋隻手一齊"},{"pid":"290c21edaf7710783c1ce2ff36601aa75dd6e303","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"可唔可以多啲人睇啊"},{"pid":"5bfaf9ffd14c35202493e638d86fab84b589d757","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:24:27.000Z","msg":"睇咗嘅推多啲俾人睇啊"},{"pid":"e008dc72d23c66ea405ec34437b16674ee53282c","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"推推推啊"},{"pid":"e85c4808643097f621c640ddb4314f656323d39e","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:25:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bad54658b79a0f7ed70e918a6743bda79a77f12","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"推到世界盡頭"},{"pid":"e800ac9bc4ceb44a062c3fddb490224908f34675","tid":1214798,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:27: